results.title: A 31-Year-Old Female With Postcoital Hemoptysis
results.text_hl: After management with @<m>CHEMICAL_Lisinopril</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D017706 @@@lisinopril@@@, she reported no new episodes of @DISEASE_Hemoptysis @DISEASE_MESH:D006469 @@@post-coital hemoptysis@@@, and a repeat chest CT showed complete resolution of the ground glass @<m>DISEASE_Corneal_Opacity</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D003318 @@@opacities@@@ bilaterally.
